name: Omni
description: Omni is more than just a cryptocurrency; it embodies the spirit of warmth and positivity, much like the adorable kitten in our logo. We are dedicated to fostering a strong, supportive community where every member feels valued and included. Our community-driven approach emphasizes the importance of collective growth and support, creating a welcoming environment for all. The kitten symbolizes the friendliness and joy we aim to bring to our users, and our focus on memes and engaging content helps to build a fun and connected community.
